data.description: $6000 in seller concession with fair offer!! Here is a gorgeous, meticulously maintained three-bedroom, two-bath, just right for today's buyer.  The open floor plan has porcelain wood-look tile throughout.  The large kitchen boasts of all stainless appliances, a gas range, granite countertops, and bar seating for at least three.  The separate dining room can be used as a home office or study because there is plenty of room in the open floor plan to accommodate a dining table off the kitchen.
